00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:23,290
Dia bertanya padamu. Katakan sesuatu!

416
00:24:32,010 --> 00:24:33,609
Dia sudah mati?

417
00:24:33,609 --> 00:24:36,540
Yah, aku rasa dia minum racun.

418
00:24:41,820 --> 00:24:43,809
Akonitin.

419
00:24:43,809 --> 00:24:46,079
Dia ternyata memang berasal dari Barat Daya.

